# =====================================================================
# 5) BoVW + PCA + KMeans (TRAIN)
#    High-level:
#      - Pre-stats on ALL images (size/brightness/etc.).
#      - Build BoVW descriptors (SIFT/ORB), pick best codebook K via AUROC.
